Azimio presidential flagbearer is the most preferred candidate in Nairobi County if elections are held today, an opinion poll by Infotrak showed on Wednesday The survey said Raila and his running ate Martha Karua have an approval rating of 49 per cent. His closest challenger, Deputy President William Ruto and his running ate Rigathi Gachagua had an approval rating of 30 per cent, according to the poll results. The opinion polls also highlighted reasons why Kenyans opted for them.